      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 37 judgment</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 37 judgment</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>家人，利女貞。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>For (the realisation of what is taught in) Jia Ren, (or for the regulation of the family), what is most advantageous is that the wife be firm and correct.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
