      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 37 六二</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 37 六二</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六二：无攸遂，在中饋，貞吉。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The second SIX, divided, shows its subject taking nothing on herself, but in her central place attending to the preparation of the food. Through her firm correctness there will be good fortune.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
