      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 37 九三</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 37 九三</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九三：家人嗃嗃，悔厲吉；婦子嘻嘻，終吝。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The third NINE, undivided, shows its subject (treating) the members of the household with stern severity. There will be occasion for repentance, there will be peril, (but) there will (also) be good fortune. If the wife and children were to be smirking and chattering, in the end there would be occasion for regret.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
