      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九五：王假有家，勿恤。吉。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fifth NINE, undivided, shows the influence of the king extending to his family. There need be no anxiety; there will be good fortune.</seg>
